title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - City Update 2 - now available
description:
In this video we will have a quick look what has been included in City Update 2. The second City Update (CU) was released earlier today and receives updates for 5 cities in throughout France as well as a special edition of Le-Bourget airport which is located close to the city of Paris.
